{"tw": {"3975510": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "CYAN BRAIN 青之腦", "steam_appid": 3975510, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4218650], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‼️本作含有暴力血腥及過激演出，請謹慎閱覽與遊玩‼️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e664d2363cfefd432f6b4347a55bd092.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未知的時間，未知的空間—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當無名少女睜開雙眼的瞬間，命運早已深深刻入她的骨髓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在未曾祈禱過的世界裡，她獨自面對那破碎不堪的機械世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無盡的殺戮與絕望的邂逅之後——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那搖曳的藍光一次次被擊碎、被奪走，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便如此，少女從未停下腳步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教堂的鐘聲迴盪於暴力與救贖的夾縫之中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當血肉與精神的極限崩毀時，世界悄然開始變貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惡夢的最深處——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >映照彼此影子的兩個靈魂終於現身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「……你，是否已準備好將自己的一切奉獻出去？」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >關於存在與湮滅、恐懼與快樂的黑暗寓言</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—《CYAN BRAIN》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/311a68cdd02eed3966eacb12cdb35d5d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=540 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e286a38702b73ec934314b481d9cac68.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《CYAN BRAIN》是一款頹廢系科幻橫向卷軸射擊遊戲。遊戲包含以下豐富內容：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>魄力滿點的射擊手感</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直面恐懼的處刑動畫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可搭乘的強力兵器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精緻的滿版動態CG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰鬥受到傷害時，衣裝會逐漸破損；攻擊命中時，將隨機噴濺出寫實的血液飛濺效果，讓演出更生動暴力。被敵人打倒時都會播放相應的處刑動畫，並在角色死亡後獲得可蒐集的死亡卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/0918dcef6d753a18da7c7bbe3cf2a693.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=1022 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可蒐集要素：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器：16種</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵人&amp;陷阱：32個</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >處刑＆色色動畫：34個</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡卡片：36張</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滿版HCG：3張</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >設有「鑑賞室」可回顧所有收藏！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊玩小提示：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吃東西將使體內水分上升，達到最大值會轉化為治療道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >彈藥快沒有的時候，記得用近戰武器擊殺敵人補充</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不想裸體外出，存檔後就能恢復</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/c6c2fb1aaeed74650e910a7b1e0eb885.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主角</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 戀鈴桃歌</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/9eb37b2e215639541b84f73431a797ad.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去記憶的少女主角。以龐大的廢墟都市為舞台，與將自己的身體改造為殺戮兵器的教會，所創造出的各種敵人與怪物展開激戰。在一次次嚴酷戰鬥中，她不斷強化自身能力，尋找並解放出嶄新的強力武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以散佈於世界各地的「記憶碎片」為線索，逐步接近這個荒廢世界的真相。與旅途中相遇的夥伴所結下的羈絆，將為少女的旅程賦予確切的意義，最終一同邁向「命運的終焉」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HS202</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 涼貴涼</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/d1f21f2654cb3ea7a526de511bd2602d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span>教會狩獵部隊的成員……不過看起來是迷路了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>L</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 御子柴泉</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/ff6731c3203fa7d5e6d017c5ba8c3407.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾是修女會成員，如今將遺留下的計劃託付給主角。將死號的殘留思念保存於特殊機器內，好將遺留下的計劃託付給主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 乙倉由依</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/f43cc720c98f82ff49efe30f8ccf265b.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出現在奇異領域中的神秘少女。以機械般、毫無感情的語氣說話。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＊遊戲為無碼版本，商店圖片僅供宣傳參考。</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‼️本作含有暴力血腥及過激演出，請謹慎閱覽與遊玩‼️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e664d2363cfefd432f6b4347a55bd092.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未知的時間，未知的空間—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當無名少女睜開雙眼的瞬間，命運早已深深刻入她的骨髓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在未曾祈禱過的世界裡，她獨自面對那破碎不堪的機械世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無盡的殺戮與絕望的邂逅之後——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那搖曳的藍光一次次被擊碎、被奪走，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便如此，少女從未停下腳步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教堂的鐘聲迴盪於暴力與救贖的夾縫之中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當血肉與精神的極限崩毀時，世界悄然開始變貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惡夢的最深處——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >映照彼此影子的兩個靈魂終於現身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「……你，是否已準備好將自己的一切奉獻出去？」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >關於存在與湮滅、恐懼與快樂的黑暗寓言</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—《CYAN BRAIN》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/311a68cdd02eed3966eacb12cdb35d5d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=540 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e286a38702b73ec934314b481d9cac68.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《CYAN BRAIN》是一款頹廢系科幻橫向卷軸射擊遊戲。遊戲包含以下豐富內容：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>魄力滿點的射擊手感</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直面恐懼的處刑動畫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可搭乘的強力兵器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精緻的滿版動態CG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰鬥受到傷害時，衣裝會逐漸破損；攻擊命中時，將隨機噴濺出寫實的血液飛濺效果，讓演出更生動暴力。被敵人打倒時都會播放相應的處刑動畫，並在角色死亡後獲得可蒐集的死亡卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/0918dcef6d753a18da7c7bbe3cf2a693.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=1022 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可蒐集要素：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器：16種</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵人&amp;陷阱：32個</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >處刑＆色色動畫：34個</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡卡片：36張</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滿版HCG：3張</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >設有「鑑賞室」可回顧所有收藏！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊玩小提示：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吃東西將使體內水分上升，達到最大值會轉化為治療道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >彈藥快沒有的時候，記得用近戰武器擊殺敵人補充</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不想裸體外出，存檔後就能恢復</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/c6c2fb1aaeed74650e910a7b1e0eb885.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主角</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 戀鈴桃歌</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/9eb37b2e215639541b84f73431a797ad.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去記憶的少女主角。以龐大的廢墟都市為舞台，與將自己的身體改造為殺戮兵器的教會，所創造出的各種敵人與怪物展開激戰。在一次次嚴酷戰鬥中，她不斷強化自身能力，尋找並解放出嶄新的強力武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以散佈於世界各地的「記憶碎片」為線索，逐步接近這個荒廢世界的真相。與旅途中相遇的夥伴所結下的羈絆，將為少女的旅程賦予確切的意義，最終一同邁向「命運的終焉」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HS202</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 涼貴涼</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/d1f21f2654cb3ea7a526de511bd2602d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span>教會狩獵部隊的成員……不過看起來是迷路了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>L</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 御子柴泉</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/ff6731c3203fa7d5e6d017c5ba8c3407.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾是修女會成員，如今將遺留下的計劃託付給主角。將死號的殘留思念保存於特殊機器內，好將遺留下的計劃託付給主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV. 乙倉由依</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/f43cc720c98f82ff49efe30f8ccf265b.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出現在奇異領域中的神秘少女。以機械般、毫無感情的語氣說話。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＊遊戲為無碼版本，商店圖片僅供宣傳參考。</strong></p>", "short_description": "《Cyan Brain 青之腦》是一款頹廢系科幻風格的橫向捲軸動作射擊遊戲。無名的她醒來，面對的是無盡的殺戮與絕望的邂逅。「……你，是否已準備好將自己的一切奉獻出去？」", "supported_languages": "日文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/44b367c1a49274a50934610aee0433ef22c0fadb/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776105488", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/6ec6819a881439a4ec49b847585543b2311ea797/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776105488", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/6ec6819a881439a4ec49b847585543b2311ea797/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776105488", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> inter Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 650 / AMD Radeon HD 7750(VRAM 1GB以上)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> inter Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 650 / AMD Radeon HD 7750(VRAM 1GB以上)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 MB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["NEKOUJI"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 28900, "final": 26000, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 289", "final_formatted": "NT$ 260"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 12 月 11 日"}}}}, "us": {"3975510": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "CYAN BRAIN", "steam_appid": 3975510, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4218650], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‼️This game contains violence, gore, and extreme content. Please read and play with caution.‼️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/d75ccb3488c73ce24150635dd73519d0.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown time. Unknown place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the nameless girl opens her eyes, her destiny is already set in motion. With no prayer nor blessing to guide her, she steps alone into a colossal ruin choked with deranged machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After unbearable despair and the unending cycle of slaughter, the wavering blue light of her will is shattered, stolen, and trampled again and again, yet she continues forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between cruelty and salvation, the tolling of the Church’s bells cuts through the world, and as their maddening echo strips away the last restraints of flesh and mind, the world begins to shift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the depths of this nightmare, she sees it:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two souls appear, reflections of each other's shadow.<br>&quot;Are you ready to make the ultimate devotion?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark fable of existence, annihilation, terror and pleasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- <i>CYAN BRAIN</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/311a68cdd02eed3966eacb12cdb35d5d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=540 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/2f9d972bbbf191d8f8658f11be34f514.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>CYAN BRAIN</i> is a decadent sci-fi side-scrolling action-shooting game.. The game includes the following:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Visceral shooting action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fear-inducing executions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mountable heavy weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Full-screen animated cinematics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you take damage in combat, your outfit will gradually tear. Successful attacks trigger random, realistic blood-splatter effects that make the action feel even more visceral. If an enemy defeats you, a unique execution animation will play, and you’ll receive a collectible Death Card upon your character’s demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/67d81bd9ddcb06eda95aec40dcf3ddb8.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=1022 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collectibles:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >weapons: 16</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies &amp; Traps: 32</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Execution &amp; H-Animations: 34</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death Cards: 36</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full-Screen HCGs: 3</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can view them all in the in-game gallery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Hints:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eating food increases your hydration. Healing items are automatically created at max hydration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your melee weapon to take out enemies when out of ammo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't want to go out in the nude, saving the game will bring back your clothes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e64bf0073c4854415bb8926f1018d48e.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Protagonist</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV: Momoka Kosuzu</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/524e90f841aefc6d60b0be99c95ea51d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl who has lost both her name and her memories. To fulfill the mission entrusted to her, she explores a vast ruined city while battling the many hostile entities created by the organization known as the Church: a group that once reshaped her body into a living weapon. Each fight sharpens her skills, strengthens her body, and leads her to new and powerful gear whose potential she gradually unlocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By following the memory fragments scattered throughout the map, she draws closer to the truth behind this devastated world. The companions she meets along the way give every step she takes through the ruins real meaning. In time, those connections will become the signposts guiding her toward the &quot;end of fate&quot; that awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HS202</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV: Ryo Suzuki</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e08da1d32742750c34370d5a21e80235.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A member of the Church's Hunting Squad, but... it seems she's gotten lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>L</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV: Izumi Mikoshiba</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/16f127748f7a11b63566bc79867a0c72.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A former  researcher of the Convent. Before her death, she preserved her lingering consciousness inside a specialized device and entrusted a certain plan to the newly awakened protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV: Yui Otokura</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/7fc0aa5cecf1669c92760d6d341260c2.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious girl who appeared within a strange domain. She speaks in a cold, mechanical, almost emotionless tone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*The final version of the game will be uncensored. Store images are for promotional reference only.</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‼️This game contains violence, gore, and extreme content. Please read and play with caution.‼️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/d75ccb3488c73ce24150635dd73519d0.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown time. Unknown place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the nameless girl opens her eyes, her destiny is already set in motion. With no prayer nor blessing to guide her, she steps alone into a colossal ruin choked with deranged machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After unbearable despair and the unending cycle of slaughter, the wavering blue light of her will is shattered, stolen, and trampled again and again, yet she continues forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between cruelty and salvation, the tolling of the Church’s bells cuts through the world, and as their maddening echo strips away the last restraints of flesh and mind, the world begins to shift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the depths of this nightmare, she sees it:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two souls appear, reflections of each other's shadow.<br>&quot;Are you ready to make the ultimate devotion?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark fable of existence, annihilation, terror and pleasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- <i>CYAN BRAIN</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/311a68cdd02eed3966eacb12cdb35d5d.avif?t=1776105488\" width=540 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/2f9d972bbbf191d8f8658f11be34f514.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>CYAN BRAIN</i> is a decadent sci-fi side-scrolling action-shooting game.. The game includes the following:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Visceral shooting action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3a0f97108cf44583312766a4ca980afa.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fear-inducing executions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/3d328dd62f1a0ca4ad6a45b9a03e8758.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mountable heavy weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/95f3fc6e122eb6077f398f3c691214ce.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Full-screen animated cinematics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.poster.avif?t=1776105488\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.webm?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/5ba5fa6ffcd61820fe63425e1d0fd8df.mp4?t=1776105488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you take damage in combat, your outfit will gradually tear. Successful attacks trigger random, realistic blood-splatter effects that make the action feel even more visceral. If an enemy defeats you, a unique execution animation will play, and you’ll receive a collectible Death Card upon your character’s demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/67d81bd9ddcb06eda95aec40dcf3ddb8.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=1022 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collectibles:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >weapons: 16</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies &amp; Traps: 32</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Execution &amp; H-Animations: 34</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death Cards: 36</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full-Screen HCGs: 3</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can view them all in the in-game gallery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Hints:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eating food increases your hydration. Healing items are automatically created at max hydration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your melee weapon to take out enemies when out of ammo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't want to go out in the nude, saving the game will bring back your clothes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/e64bf0073c4854415bb8926f1018d48e.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >