?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A former  researcher of the Convent. Before her death, she preserved her lingering consciousness inside a specialized device and entrusted a certain plan to the newly awakened protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>CV: Yui Otokura</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/extras/7fc0aa5cecf1669c92760d6d341260c2.avif?t=1776105488\" width=1560 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious girl who appeared within a strange domain. She speaks in a cold, mechanical, almost emotionless tone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*The final version of the game will be uncensored. Store images are for promotional reference only.</strong></p>", "short_description": "Cyan Brain is a decadent sci-fi side-scrolling action shooter. Awaken to face endless slaughter and desperate encounters. &quot;Are you ready to make the ultimate devotion?&quot;", "supported_languages": "Japanese<strong>*</strong>, English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Korean<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/a4c772fc338c3614848584c31859b2652241e435/header.jpg?t=1776105488", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/d8960629c94b1bc0b1c10effca243637de473fe7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1776105488", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3975510/d8960629c94b1bc0b1c10effca243637de473fe7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1776105488", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br